    <!-- Info dialog -->
    <string name="info" translatable="false"><![CDATA[
        <h1>About</h1>
        <p>Simple Counter is a <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tally_counter">tally counter</a> for Android.
        It makes counting easier. You can have multiple counters with their own names and values.
        Values can be changed using volume buttons.</p>
        <p>This is an open source application. Source code is hosted on GitHub at
        <a href="https://github.com/Tsukanov/Simple-Counter/">https://github.com/Tsukanov/Simple-Counter/</a>.</p>
        <p>This is my first Android application. The goal was to make something useful and easy to build.
        Feel free to submit bug reports <a href="https://github.com/Tsukanov/Simple-Counter/issues">on GitHub</a>.</p>
        <p>I hope you\'ll find this app useful!</p>

        <h2>Contributing</h2>
        <p>Feel free to make improvements and create pull requests. If you want to help with translation go to project\'s
        <a href="http://crowdin.net/project/simple-counter">page on Crowdin</a>.</p>
        <p>Thanks to all contributors who help me work on this small and interesting project.</p>

